data.description: CHARMING home in a desirable location featuring an expansive backyard making it great for entertaining. Plenty of room for an outdoor kitchen, tiki hut and pool. Comfortable 3bd/2ba ground level concrete home, open living floor plan, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, new water heater, new central a/c, and fenced in yard providing lots of privacy. Large storage shed. Close to good restaurants and shopping. You will enjoy the open water Atlantic Ocean views from the front yard!
